            {
              "type": "ReferenceGroup",
              "primaryrefs": [
                {
                  "type": "Reference",
                  "refclass": "A",
                  "comment": "The picture of ``bearing fruit'' may cover many aspects of Christian life but it includes that of developing Christian character, effective Christian service and mission. These result, not from human effort, but from abiding in Christ.",
